Uses of Package
nzilbb.encoding

  • Packages that use nzilbb.encoding 
    Package Description
    nzilbb.encoding
    Handling for translation between different phoneme encodings.
  • Classes in nzilbb.encoding used by nzilbb.encoding 
    Class Description
    CMU2DISC
    Translates CMU-encoded phonemic transcriptions like T R AE2 N S K R IH1 P SH AH0 N to CELEX-DISC-encoded transcriptions like tr{nskrIpSVn.
    DISC2CMU
    Translates CELEX-DISC-encoded transcriptions like tr{nskrIpSVn to CMU-encoded phonemic transcriptions like T R AE N S K R IH P SH AH N.
    DISC2IPA
    Translates CELEX-DISC-encoded transcriptions like tr{nskrIpS@n to IPA-encoded phonemic transcriptions using Unicode characters like t…π√¶nsk…π…™p É…ôn.
    IPA2DISC
    Translates IPA-encoded phonemic transcriptions using Unicode characters like t…π√¶nsk…π…™p É…ôn to CELEX-DISC-encoded transcriptions like tr{nskrIpS@n
    PhonemeTranslator
    Base-class for Functions that convert phonemic transcriptions from one encoding to another.
